    "content": "<h2>Cívky a kondenzátory</h2>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 460 130' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <rect x='20' y='15' width='190' height='100' rx='8' fill='#eff6ff' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='115' y='35' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='12'>Cívka (induktor)</text>\n  <path d='M50,80 Q61,55 72,80' fill='none' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2.5'/><path d='M72,80 Q83,55 94,80' fill='none' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2.5'/><path d='M94,80 Q105,55 116,80' fill='none' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2.5'/><path d='M116,80 Q127,55 138,80' fill='none' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2.5'/><path d='M138,80 Q149,55 160,80' fill='none' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2.5'/><path d='M160,80 Q171,55 182,80' fill='none' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2.5'/>\n  <text x='115' y='105' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>L [henry, H]</text>\n  <rect x='250' y='15' width='190' height='100' rx='8' fill='#f0fdf4' stroke='#22c55e' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='345' y='35' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#166534' font-size='12'>Kondenzátor</text>\n  <line x1='310' y1='55' x2='310' y2='95' stroke='#22c55e' stroke-width='3'/><line x1='330' y1='55' x2='330' y2='95' stroke='#22c55e' stroke-width='3'/>\n  <line x1='280' y1='75' x2='310' y2='75' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='330' y1='75' x2='360' y2='75' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <text x='290' y='55' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>+</text><text x='340' y='55' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>−</text>\n  <text x='370' y='70' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>Q = C · U</text>\n  <text x='345' y='105' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>C [farad, F]</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Cívka (induktor)</h3>\n<p><strong>Cívka</strong> je navinutý vodič. V obvodu se střídavým proudem se „brání\" změnám proudu (<strong>induktance</strong>).</p>\n<p>Značka induktance: <strong>L</strong>, jednotka: <strong>henry (H)</strong>.</p>\n<p>Využití: filtry, transformátory, tlumivky, elektromagnety.</p>\n<h3>Kondenzátor</h3>\n<p><strong>Kondenzátor</strong> uchovává elektrický náboj. Skládá se ze dvou vodivých desek oddělených izolantem (dielektrikem).</p>\n<p>Značka kapacity: <strong>C</strong>, jednotka: <strong>farad (F)</strong>.</p>\n<div class='formula'>$$Q = C \\cdot U$$</div>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Veličina</th><th>Symbol</th><th>Jednotka</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>náboj</td><td>Q</td><td>C (coulomb)</td></tr>\n<tr><td>kapacita</td><td>C</td><td>F (farad)</td></tr>\n<tr><td>napětí</td><td>U</td><td>V</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>Využití: vyhlazování napětí, časovače, filtry, startér zářivky.</p>"
  }
}
